issue.title: Northeast-bound bikes whose angle points into Q4 of the Cartesian plane turn immediately
issue.body:
The value of cos(travelAngle) is inaccurate due to travelAngle's being a reference angle.

Is a problem until we receive sponsorship from Google Maps API.
